      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm a bit confused. I'm not looking for metaphors or anything. I just need to know the actual legal risk. If I sign this, am I personally on the hook for their legal fees if they get sued because of something I did? Can you explain the actual financial consequences without the analogies?",
